c Header file for camvib and camiso to set
c up the size of the problem they can treat.
C All parameters are a function of the maximum number of atoms.
C 31 April 1997 - AJT
C 19 March 1999  Size increased - IHW
C 16 March 2004  Size increased again!  - IHW

      parameter(MAXNAT =1000)

C  These should not be touched
      parameter(MAXNC  =MAXNAT * 3)
      parameter(MAXNI  =MAXNAT * 3 + MAXNAT / 2)
      parameter(MAXNINT=MAXNC  - 6)
      parameter(MAXDIAG=MAXNC * MAXNC / 2 + (MAXNC *3 ) / 2 )
      parameter(MAXAPO =MAXNAT + 1)

C for Camiso

      parameter(MAXFCMS =MAXDIAG * 3)
      parameter(MAXXYZ = MAXNAT * 10)

